---
title: Portuguese Style Chicken with Roasted Red Pepper, Couscous and Minty Yogurt Dip
description: On the table in thirty minutes, packed with deliciously fresh and earthy flavours, and requiring minimal prep and washing up, our Portuguese style chicken makes a great midweek recipe. Cooking the peppers under the chicken thighs not only gives them an extra delicious flavour, but it also means you only have 1 baking tray to wash up. Winner winner, chicken dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/portuguese-style-chicken-797ec586.jpg
